---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Compliance & Safety | Free AI Tools" 
  description="Our commitment to providing a safe, compliant, and family-friendly index of open-source AI models.">
  <main class="container max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 sm:py-24">
    <header class="text-center mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black tracking-tighter text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
        Compliance & Safety
      </h1>
    </header>

    <div class="prose dark:prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
      <p>
        At Free AI Tools, we are committed to maintaining a safe and compliant platform. Our automated systems are designed to filter and exclude any content that could be considered Not Safe For Work (NSFW), explicit, or otherwise inappropriate. We strive to create a resource that is accessible and useful for everyone, including students, researchers, and professionals.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you encounter any content that you believe violates this policy, please contact us through our <a href="https://github.com/mosesy5688-cell/ai-nexus/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub issues page</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>